Merger_Coll_PosY2       8432.28                  # Y-center   of cluster 2 in kpc
Merger_Coll_VelX2       -900.0                   # X-velocity of cluster 2 in km/s
Merger_Coll_VelY2       0.0                      # Y-velocity of cluster 2 in km/s
Merger_Coll_IsGas2      1                        # If cluster 2 should have gas and not have DM only
Bondi_MassBH2           1.54692010347e10         # black hole mass (in Msun)
